AGI - Political, administrative and judicial earthquake in Liguria Region >, where with the charge of corruption was arrested and led to the domiciles President Giovanni Toti >. This morning the soldiers of the Provincial Command of the Guardia di Finanza of Genoa have given execution to a series of ordinances of application of precautionary measures against not only the governor, but also of Paolo Emilio Signorini>, former president of the harbour Authority of System of the Western Ligurian Sea and to Iren, the entrepreneur Aldo Spinelli>, former patron of Genoa and Livorno.
&nbsp;
Mr.ini's prison was set up, while for the other three domiciles. Precautionary measures are also taken for Roberto Spinelli, entrepreneur in the logistic and real estate sector, recipient of the interdictive measure of the temporary ban to exercise the entrepreneurial and professional activity, accused of corruption against the President of the Liguria Region; Mauro Vianello>, entrepreneur working in the field of the Port of Genoa (destinator of the interdictive measure of the temporary prohibition to exercise the business and professional activity, accused of corruption against Paolo Emilio Signorini); Francesco Moncada>, director of Esselunga S.p.A., also temporarily interrupted, accused of corruption against the President of the Liguria Region.
<h2> The origins of the survey
An investigation that unites several threads, which lights the spotlight on the rooting of organized crime in Liguria and that puts in the center the governor, suspended from his assignment and already replaced with the vice president of the Region, Alessandro Piana>. The investigation, coordinated directly by the prosecutor Nicola Piacente along with the additions Francesco Pinto and Vittorio Ranieri Miniati and the substitutes Luca Monteverde and Federico Manotti, started in 2020 from a hypothesis of electoral corruption >formulata from the Procura della Spezia and coordinated by the chief prosecutor of the Spezia Antonio Patrono and the deputy Elisa Loris. It was the Prosecutor of La Spezia to transmit the acts to that Genoese, which in turn has discovered a new jar of Pandora. The clues to the inquiries were collected thanks to interceptions and monitoring activities.
&nbsp;
The investigation, as said initially concentrated on hypotheses of electoral corruption, has subsequently developed on specific events regarding financing, considered illicit, for the political compagine head to the president of the Liguria Region, issues of various usefulness in favor of the former president of the Harbour System Authority of the Western Ligurian Sea, and the identification of the prompted determinations, promises and/or adopted by the inquiries in front of the financings and the utilities received. In the order, already sent to the anti-Mafia parliamentary commission, it emerges that Matteo Cozzani "agì on mandate received by Giovanni Toti during the election campaign of 2020, along with the brothers Testa, representatives of the genoese Riesine community", writes the gip Paola Faggioni of the Tribunal of Genoa, in the order that has led to the arrest, among others of the Ligurian governor.
&nbsp;
Cozzani, former mayor of Portovenere and chief of cabinet of Toti is under house arrest. "Cozzani - continues - as coordinator of the list "Let's change with Toti president", has acted to obtain to advantage of the list of the candidate president Giovanni Toti and of some candidates, Ilario Cavo, Laura Lauro and Stefano Anzalone, the vote of the members of the Riesine community of Genoa, promising to voters, through the brothers Testa, as a counterpart essentially places of work destined to the same voters, or to people with these tied by friends. This happened through agreements and agreements that Cozzani signed on 'mandato' of Toti.'
Reports with clans
It is precisely the figure of the Heads to sanction, once again the presence of organized crime > in Liguria, deeply rooted in the territory and with many links with local politics and entrepreneurship. Abandoning traditional raw methods, "the Sicilian Mafia association has developed a kind of careful camouflage, aimed on the one hand to make difficult the collection of evidence by the pollutants, on the other to avoid strong counterproductive social alarm", writes the gip. In this case, "electoral corrutteles have been realized on occasions of electoral consultations of 20 and 21 September 2020 and have involved subjects close to the environments of the family of Riesi>, mafia consortery rooted in Genoa in the district of Certosa".
&nbsp;
The presence of riesini in the province of Genoa is already rooted since 1985, as certifies a judgment of the Court of Liguria. The riesini, regarding the earthquake in Liguria Region, are the brothers Testa: Arturo Angelo Testa and Italo Maurizio Testa, recipients of the obligation to reside in the Municipality of Boltiere, accused of the offence of electoral corruption, aggravated by article 416-bis.1 c.p. as committed in order to facilitate the activity of the Mafia association Cosa Nostra, especially the Cammarata clan of the Mandamento di Riesi with projection in the city of Genoa.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
The twins were also recalled during the planning of the election campaign of mayor Marco Bucci>. In a phone call intercepted on 13 February 2022, intersected between Toti, Bucci and Cozzani, talking about the resources for the electoral campaign (estimated in 250 thousand euros), the governor calls into question the riesini. But the name, writes the gip, "exit a worried reaction from Cozzani" that declares " stay away from those there, they put us in jail."
<h2> The harbour world trema</h2>
An investigation that makes the harbour world tremble and one of the leading kermesses of Liguria: the nautical exhibition >. In fact there are also the president of Confindustria nautica, Saverio Cecchi, and the commercial director of the nautical exhibition of Genoa, Alessandro Campagna, in the list of inquiries for corruption from the Procura della Spezia, in the wake of the investigation mother of Genoa. For Cecchi and Campagna the prohibition of business activities and offices has been taken, to exercise professions, enterprises or management offices. The precautionary measures taken in Genoa were detailed by the gip in the order from more than 600 pages: for Giovanni Toti are taken for "the actual concrete danger that the investigation commits other serious crimes", in particular "that can reiterate on the occasion of the next elections analogous conducts corruttive, putting to its function in the service of private interests in exchange for itself and for others". Such precautionary requirements "are essentially deusible from the very methods of conduct from which an evident systematic nature of the corruptive mechanism is transposed".
&nbsp;
The gip adds that "the present and concrete danger of probatory pollution is also considered to exist," that the investigation "takes into contact with other investigations to develop a common strategy", or that contacts people "can provide useful circumstances for the purpose of a convenient reconstruction of events". For Cozzani, the precautionary requirements (to domiciles) are also applied on the basis of the "surprising involvement manifested in carrying out the conduits". For Spinelli, he too at the domiciles, "the judge speaks of "evident systematicism of the corruptive mechanism for the attainment of its entrepreneurial interests". Still more serious the picture for the ad of Iren, Paolo Emilio Signorini, only in prison: the gip speaks of a "personality completely incurring of the public interest and the principles of impartiality and good performance of the public function carried out, made available and service of private interests in order to obtain ius change personal usefulness (balance of the expenses for the wedding of the daughter, luxury stays, promises of prestigious work assignments)". &nbsp;
&nbsp;
For the judge is " alarming the systematicity of the corruttivo mechanism, placed in existence in a wide temporal arc and with two different harbour entrepreneurs, demonstrating a poor awareness of the very important publicist role covered".
<h2> For mayor Bucci "there is a city to carry on"</h2>
Meanwhile, while Pd and M5S call for resignation of Toti and his team, from the regional junta and the mayor of Genoa, Marco Bucci, comes a levata of shields: "There is a city to move forward with a strategic plan, very precise and 7 billion to land and to sea - said the first citizen - On this we move forward at speed perhaps even greater. The message is that you have to do things, do them even better and of course be careful that there is no pollution. I'm just saying that we will do everything we can, because we don't block the institutions, indeed it must be a message to move forward. Then I'm guaranteed, of course, and so I want to wait for all the judgements. And anyway, in any case, full confidence in the judiciary." &nbsp;
&nbsp;
Bucci added that "I comment what is my part, that is the part of the city and what our administrations have to do for the city, which will continue not only at the same speed as before, with the same tenacity as before and the same force as before, but perhaps even more, just to show that things must be done well. Do you remember what I said after the Morandi collapse? That day I said the city is not on its knees. Even now neither of us is on our knees, indeed, we are standing and with even greater energy, because we want to show that things are doing well." Finally, "from the human point of view can only make me sorry, but maybe there is nothing, so it is useless to make these comments now because they have little sense. What makes sense now is to say that we have to carry out things and do them as best as possible."
&nbsp;
For the regional Councillor at Urbanism, Marco Scajola, very loyal to Toti and exponent of his list, Toti is "a person we believe honest, correct, who works daily in the interest of Liguria. We hope that this sad story can be clarified as soon as possible and can, in the shortest possible time, return to the work that is carrying out with great determination and great courage. Liguria in these years has changed, it is under the eyes of all. The whole committee is cohesive." But there are already those who, like FdI, the historic leader of the coalition, evaluates resignations. Toti will be watching from his home in Ameglia this time. The lawyer Stefano Savi said he will be able to explain everything. He, for his part, claims to be "tranquillissimo". &nbsp;

